text: "Lavender Haze" is an electropop/R&B; song by American singer-songwriter Taylor Swift. It is released on November 29, 2022. It is from her tenth studio album, Midnights. The lyrics of the song are about eroticism, and reference her desire to be in a romantic relationship without all the exterior scrutiny and pressure. It peaked at number two on the US Billboard Hot 100, blocked from the top spot by the album's lead single, "Anti-Hero". ==References== Category:2022 songs Category:Taylor Swift songs Category:Electropop songs Category:R&B; songs
